title: Does Rep. Ocasio-Cortez Have a Low Credit Score, Closed Checking Accounts, and a History of Evictions?
subtitle: You can claim anything you want if your audience is unconcerned with matters such as evidence.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: Congresswoman Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez has experienced two "sheriff evictions," two closed checking accounts, and a credit score of 430.
